{"tid":2101769,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：學校可自行決定何時放暑假","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:58:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"763a0d234112172acf61b9a2e482b368eb9c42cf","tid":2101769,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"多名議員在立法會衛生事務委員會上關注，教育局會否宣布全港學校因應疫情停課。其中陳凱欣指，部份學校將暑假延後至7月底才開始，近一、兩星期正值學校考試期間，亦有學校的小五呈分試考試日期未明，反問教育局有否考慮學生和家長的情況。<br />\n<br />\n出席會議的教育局首席教育主任劉穎賢回應指，學校在取得法團校董會同意後，可以自行決定何時放暑假，強調當局會與衛生防護中心繼續溝通，決定是否要採取進一步措施。食物及衛生局長陳肇始則表示，根據最新評估，教育局會有所宣布。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346405&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=105ab4d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346405</a>"},{"pid":"619a9b54f9bdafea77a5edbf42e4b2e18d5586d9","tid":2101769,"uid":152944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"乜陳凱欣仲係議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cd8fa192a836e04b4bccba51ccdf27108ef373","tid":2101769,"uid":234357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"619a9b54f9bdafea77a5edbf42e4b2e18d5586d9","tid":2101769,"uid":152944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"乜陳凱欣仲係議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"投訴商台"},{"pid":"ee358fa425d0762a532a50ebe196cbb45e6315d0","tid":2101769,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢自行決定？咁出人工請你做乜？"},{"pid":"7dd787512395b678b31f21eb69c233958f858ec5","tid":2101769,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"即放去到12月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\